	  <div class="forum-post-info clearfix">	
	    	    	    
	  </div>     
      <div class="forum-post-content">
        
  <div class="field-body view-mode-full">
    <p>Hi</p><p>  Is there any plans to support firefox OS platform for Alljoyn. I have built Javascript plugin and used it to test javascript-based app using a browser on linux ( I also see android there as an option). But any pointers on how can we make it work on firefox OS based devices. I believe alljoyn daemon functionality needs to be ported to javascript and use mozilla open web APIs?</p>  </div>
      </div>

      
